entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Dakk crafted you armor made from an Acklay's shell.
entries.journal_entry_description: You must gather all the other parts needed to complete the armor.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The fur from these beasts is perfectly suited to keep its wearer comfortable in the most extreme temperatures.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Gather Fur from Mountain Tusk Cats
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Peko Peko feathers are needed to pad the pointed edges of the armor. Gather 10 feathers.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Feral Shaupaut hide is best suited for the leather ties used to piece the armor together. You must gather 10 pieces of undamaged hide.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Gather the Hide from Feral Shaupauts
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You are instructed to gather all the other ingredients needed to complete the armor.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return with all the components you have gathered.
